  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb3 \u0b89\u0bb2\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf - \u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb9\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Underworld Gunman Killed in Police Firing - Incident in Gampaha Pemmulla",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Outer Fort - An underworld suspect has been shot dead by the police in a shooting incident that left an ex-serviceman dead near the entrance of the private bus stand in Bastian Mawtha.",
        "The police said that the suspect was killed in the firing by the officers of the Colombo Crime Prevention Unit in the Yakkala-Pemulla area of \u200b\u200bGampaha District and the 41-year-old Ihala Withanake Joseph Kumar from Elpitiya area has died.",
        "An ex-army soldier was killed in the early morning of May 30 by unknown persons near the entrance gate of Purak Fort - Bastian Mawatha private bus station, within sight of the Colombo Deputy Inspector General's office. Another ex-serviceman was also injured.",
        "It is suspected that this gunfire targeted a relative of the person who was killed in Aluthgama on June 3, and that the army soldiers who were returning from a case may have been the target of the shooting due to a change of identity.",
        "Those who carried out the said shooting, went from Kurakottai in front of Fort Railway Station and reached Lake House Circle and from there DR. Organized crime investigation unit of CCD has revealed that Wijewardana fled towards Marudhan through Mawat and the number plate of the motorcycle they used was fake.",
        "According to the investigations carried out in this situation, the organized crime investigation unit of the CCD has received information that the suspect related to the shooting in the outskirts is hiding in the Gampaha area.",
        "According to the information received after this, while the police were going towards Gampaha in a white van, the suspect was caught by the police while traveling on a motorcycle at Memmullai area. The police said that the suspect fired at the police with his Re 56 gun, and the suspect died in the retaliatory attack.",
        "The van in which the police was traveling was damaged by the suspect's firing."
      ],
